text: Burgynbash () is a rural locality (a village) in Kurdymsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 137 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 5 km from Stary Kurdym. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Burgynbash
